QueryText: asked about rice drum seeder
KccAns: 1. Seed rate required - 15 kg per acre2. Time required for direct seeding - 120 minutes (2 hours)3. Labour required - 3 persons [one for pulling the drum seeder, one to help the puller to lift the machine at the end of the field, and one to fill/refill the seed in the drums].4.
